comments: Can\'t understand a word he says. He\'s writing is difficult to read. Try not to take him if you want to learn anything.

If you are good at doing labs without direction from an instructor, take Joshi. He has a horribly thick accent and messy handwriting. You cant understand anything he says, but he is an easy grader and will help you as much as he can... if you can understand him. He\'s a nice guy, but dont take him if you need clarification on lab procedures.
